data.title: Medical School
data.meta_description: uerm Medicine - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document provides information for applicants to the College of Medicine at University of the East Ramon Magsaysay Memorial Medical Center. It outlines the requirements for application including transcripts, diploma, moral character references, National Medical Admission Test scores, and application fees. The deadline for application submission is listed as December 21, 2012. Minimum requirements are described as holding a baccalaureate degree and undergoing an interview. Requirements for enrollment if accepted are also specified.
